fields.calculatedFormula:
IF(Admin_Assigned_Completer__c = TRUE, "Completer",

IF(Admin_Assigned_Attendance__c = TRUE, "Participant",


IF(Workshop__r.Completer_Set_by_User__c = TRUE && ISPICKVAL(Mandatory_Session__c, "Yes"), "Completer",
IF(Workshop__r.Completer_Set_by_User__c = TRUE && ISPICKVAL(Mandatory_Session__c, "No"), "Participant",

IF(Workshop__r.Completer_Set_by_User__c = TRUE && ISPICKVAL(Mandatory_Session__c, "") && Session_Count__c > 0, "Participant",
IF(Workshop__r.Completer_Set_by_User__c = TRUE && ISPICKVAL(Mandatory_Session__c, ""), "Enrolled",

IF(Session_Count__c = 0, "Enrolled",

IF(ISNULL(Workshop__r.Number_of_Sessions_for_a_Completer__c) && Session_Count__c > 0, "Participant",

IF( Workshop__r.Number_of_Sessions_for_a_Completer__c > Session_Count__c, "Participant",

IF( Workshop__r.Number_of_Sessions_for_a_Completer__c <= Session_Count__c
&& (IF(ISNULL(Capable_Handyworker_Sessions__c), 0, Capable_Handyworker_Sessions__c) >= IF(ISNULL(Workshop__r.Number_of_Handyworker_Sessions__c), 0, Workshop__r.Number_of_Handyworker_Sessions__c)
&& IF(ISNULL(Capable_OT_Sessions__c), 0, Capable_OT_Sessions__c) >= IF(ISNULL(Workshop__r.Number_of_Occupational_Health_Sessions__c), 0, Workshop__r.Number_of_Occupational_Health_Sessions__c)
&& IF(ISNULL(Capable_RN_Sessions__c), 0, Capable_RN_Sessions__c) >= IF(ISNULL(Workshop__r.Number_of_Registered_Nurse_Sessions__c), 0, Workshop__r.Number_of_Registered_Nurse_Sessions__c)), "Completer",
"Participant"))))))))))
